 API Security Risk Analysis – ReqRes Demo API

 Project Overview
This repository documents a **read-only API Security Risk Analysis** conducted on the ReqRes testing environment ([https://reqres.in](https://reqres.in)).  
The objective was to simulate the **initial discovery phase** of a security audit, identifying misconfigurations and risks associated with modern SaaS API integrations.

